Apply clustering in a dataset

cluster_s1.Rd

Create 5 separate cluster datasets from a dataframe (for k = 2,3,4,5,6)

cluster_s1(final_dataset = cluster_data_all)

Arguments

final_dataset

Specify the dataframe

Details

  • Must provide a dataframe with a categorical variable (first variable) and 2 or more continuous variables

  • The provided dataframe cannot include missing values

Examples


library(tidyverse)
